<!-- 
   {#
   Page: search.html
   Purpose: Page is displayed when a shop has manual payment enabled.
   Status: Required
   This Template is Passed to the layout.html as {{ content }}
   CSS Notes: 
      
   Variables on This Page:
   
   {{ results }}
    Description: Results set from Django Market's Search. Must be displayed as is, no alterations
   
   {{ paginator }}
    Description: If the search results are > 20 , this page will paginated, this variable must be included. 
    
   Filters on this Page
   |length
    Description: Jinga filter that reports the length of the results set. This is used on this page to query for no results, so an alternative can be displayed. 
    
   Variable to iterate over
   None
   
   Author: Stephen Power
   #}
   -->